This paper deals with the problem of identifying malicious web domains using machine learning techniques. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of online credibility and performance data, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI).
